  {
    "client_msg_id": "f2b4cf0a-f16b-4f6b-a6d1-51a5ce53f85f",
    "type": "message",
    "text": "I think this gets to the essence of the power of computers. People in all walks of life get to walk around with half-formed desires, act on some of them and find out years and decades later how wrong they were. Computers are super powers for finding out immediately how wrong we are.",
    "user": "UCUSW7WVD",
