  {
    "client_msg_id": "36484410-f07c-4f9a-99fc-7efd09cd14bc",
    "type": "message",
    "text": "You're right that we often don't know what we really want, but you can modify the program as you go. Again by just thinking the change in the model you want.\n\nSo then it also becomes a wiki of our every design thought. A personal memo pad extraordinaire. Yes, like writing not only records ideas but also helps us clarify them and generate new ones. Just on steroids.",
    "user": "U02R1V54SV9",
    "ts": "1639939263.290000",
